# ─── Site-specific plugins (optional) ────────────────────────────────────────
# Path to an external plugin root scanned in addition to plugins/.
# Use this to ship plugins that should ONLY exist on a specific site
# without versioning them in the shared monorepo.
# Leave UNSET on sites that do not host site-specific plugins.
# Example (POOLP site only):
# EXTERNAL_PLUGINS_DIR=/var/poolp-plugins
